Header.Name: EDM
Header.Description: Metadata profile for the European Data Model (EDM). See http://pro.europeana.eu/page/edm-documentation

CMD_Element.name: dc-description
CMD_Element.Documentation: A description of the CHO

CMD_Element.name: dc-format
CMD_Element.Documentation: Use for the terms generally applied to indicate the format of the cultural heritage object or the file format of a born digital object. Use the value ?3DVPDF? if appropriate.

CMD_Element.name: dc-identifier
CMD_Element.Documentation: An identifier of the original CHO

CMD_Element.name: dc-language
CMD_Element.Documentation: The language of text CHOs and also for other types of CHO if there is a language aspect.

CMD_Element.name: dc-relation
CMD_Element.Documentation: The name or identifier of a related resource, generally used for other related CHOs

CMD_Element.name: dc-rights
CMD_Element.Documentation: The name of the rights holder of the CHO if possible or for more general rights information.

CMD_Element.name: dc-source
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource from which the described resource is derived in whole or in part i.e. the source of the original CHO.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-alternative
CMD_Element.Documentation: Any alternative title of the CHO including abbreviations or translations that may not be exact.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-conformsTo
CMD_Element.Documentation: An established standard to which the CHO conforms.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-extent
CMD_Element.Documentation: The size or duration of the CHO.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-hasVersion
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another, later resource that is a version, edition or adaptation of the CHO demonstrating substantive changes in content rather than format.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-isFormatOf
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another resource that is substantially the same as the CHO but in another format.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-isPartOf
CMD_Element.Documentation: A resource in which the CHO is physically or logically included.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-isReferencedBy
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another resource that references, cites or otherwise points to the CHO.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-isReplacedBy
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another resource that supplants , displaces, or supersedes the CHO.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-isRequiredBy
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another related resource that requires the CHO to support its function, delivery or coherence.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-isVersionOf
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another, earlier resource of which the CHO is a version, edition or adaptation, demonstrating substantive changes in content rather than format.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-medium
CMD_Element.Documentation: The material or physical carrier of the CHO

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-provenance
CMD_Element.Documentation: A statement of changes in ownership and custody of the CHO since its creation. Significant for authenticity, integrity and interpretation.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-references
CMD_Element.Documentation: Other resources referenced, cited or otherwise pointed to by the CHO.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-replaces
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is supplanted, displaced, or superseded by the CHO.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-requires
CMD_Element.Documentation: Another resource that is required by the described resource to support its function, delivery or coherence.

CMD_Element.name: dcterms-tableOfContents
CMD_Element.Documentation: A list of sub-units of the CHO.

CMD_Element.name: edm-incorporates
